  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "14 kilos of turtle meat is caught in Silawatura",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy said that two persons were arrested with 14 kg of turtle meat in Silavathura Kayakkuli area of \u200b\u200bMannar.",
        "The Navy says that the two suspects were arrested along with the stock of turtle meat found on the coast of the Kayakkuli Coastal Monitoring Center of the Sri Lanka Naval Ship Theraputta, which belongs to the North West Naval Command. .",
        "The Navy further said that the suspects, the stock of turtle meat and the dinghy were handed over to the Madu Wildlife Department office for further investigations."
      ],
